<!--TEXT PROPERTIES
1.text-align:left,center,right,justify

2.text-indent:giving indentation(giving space at staring of paragraph)

3.text-transform:text into another format
uppercase,lowercase,capitalize

4.letter-spacing giving space between letter to letter in pixels
if negetive spacing given, then each letter overlaps

5.word-spacing-giving space between word to word in pixels

6.line-height-giving space between line to line

7.text-decoration:giving underlines,overline,line-through,none
-->
<!--<html>
